ve mixing (SFWM) source. Finally, we note that our technique can easily\nbe extended to systems with multiple ground states and generalized scattering\nproblems with both finite photon number input and coherent state drive,\npotentially enhancing the understanding of, e.g., light-matter entanglement and\nphoton phase gates.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 8 Oct 2017 19:45:35 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 4 Nov 2017 00:55:12 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 17 Nov 2017 00:49:15 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Sat, 19 May 2018 17:52:58 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-05-30"}
