exotic states, the large-$N_c$ consistency conditions require two narrow\nflavor-exotic states, each of these states coupling dominantly to one specific\nmeson-meson channel.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 9 Oct 2017 12:56:25 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-10-26"}
